sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Operator as DEV operator
  participant Workbench as DEV Workbench
  participant Backend as DEV backend
  participant Registry as Stage registry
  participant Chat as Stage-bound chat
  participant Generator
  participant Reviewer
  participant Evidence as Evidence store

  Operator->>Workbench: Start or resume stage run
  Workbench->>Backend: Run stage with stage_id
  Backend->>Registry: Resolve stage branch and worktree
  Registry-->>Backend: Validated workspace and AgentConfiguration
  Backend->>Chat: Bind session to stage metadata
  Chat->>Generator: Execute next implementation turn
  Generator->>Chat: Changes, tests, and notes
  Chat->>Reviewer: Review generated output
  alt reviewer requests follow-up
    Reviewer-->>Chat: {"status":"continue","summary":"..."}
    Chat->>Generator: Follow-up prompt with bounded context
  else reviewer completes
    Reviewer-->>Chat: {"status":"complete","summary":"..."}
    Chat->>Evidence: Persist changed files, tests, risks, checklist, reviewer state
    Chat-->>Backend: Final user-facing summary
  end
  Backend-->>Workbench: Stage state and evidence

